    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>The Little Professor Syndrome</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Rick Kresse letter praises Lawrence Osborne's June 18 article on Asperger's syndrome0</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>I am the parent of a 6-year-old with Asperger's syndrome. One highlight of my Father's Day was reading Lawrence Osborne's article (June 18). His observations, coupled with the photos by Judith Joy Ross, captured the essence of this complex condition.</p>
        <p>My wife and I look forward to the day our son will make his contribution to society and society will, in return, see beyond his unconventional ways of dealing with life.</p>
        <p>Rick Kresse  Chicago</p>
      </block>
